lastVersion.statementHTML:
Goal

Just have a look to the string S and try find the algorithm to get a readable output.
Input
line 1 string S of words or signs, separated by spaces.
Output
One word in upper case
Constraints
2 <= length S <= 10000
Example
Input
higHlIght
Output
HI
